@Node "sysreq" "System requirements"

This printerdriver should work with any Amiga. It has been made and
tested on a Amiga 500 with 1 Mb.
@EndNode

@Node "install" "Install the printerdriver"

To install the printerdriver simply drag the program named
"Stylus300" (this is the printerdriver) to your "devs:printers/"-
directory and select Stylus300 as printerdriver in preferences.

Note: the default-charactertable of your Stylus300 should be set to
      PC 850 (Multilingual), see @{"extended characters" Link "extchars"} for more
      information.
@EndNode

